    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed. Achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for MRL 5 across all factor categories. Monte Carlo UQ confirms 95th-percentile hemolysis index remains 18% below clinical threshold. Output comparison demonstrates adequate agreement across all 5 operating points. The ContextOfUse description details the operating parameter ranges (temperature, pressure, flow rate, rotational speed, flow regime) under which predictions are valid, and the assessment team considers these ranges sufficient to characterise model applicability. Decision: Accepted.",
